confirm that A-1

- A - I4 provides a 4 x 4 matrix of zeros.

 A<-diag(c(2,3,5,-1))
> A
     [,1] [,2] [,3] [,4]
[1,]    2    0    0    0
[2,]    0    3    0    0
[3,]    0    0    5    0
[4,]    0    0    0   -1
> 
> A_inv<-solve(A)
> A_inv
     [,1]      [,2] [,3] [,4]
[1,]  0.5 0.0000000  0.0    0
[2,]  0.0 0.3333333  0.0    0
[3,]  0.0 0.0000000  0.2    0
[4,]  0.0 0.0000000  0.0   -1
> 
> I4<-diag(4)
> I4
     [,1] [,2] [,3] [,4]
[1,]    1    0    0    0
[2,]    0    1    0    0
[3,]    0    0    1    0
[4,]    0    0    0    1
> 
> result<-A_inv - A- I4
> result
     [,1]      [,2] [,3] [,4]
[1,] -2.5  0.000000  0.0    0
